<.decorative_heading tag="h3" style="simpler">Challenges</.decorative_heading>

<p>
  There were a few challenges when building out this project. The first was porting over existing content from the original site, including hundreds of blog posts. This meant collaborating with designers and back-end developers to ensure both the templates and data structures accounted for everything the old content included, and providing fallbacks for new design elements when necessary.
</p>

<p>
  Another challenge with the new site was finding a way for the Foundation to highlight each organization they've supported. We were able to create a templated structure that each nonprofit could fill out with some basic information on their organization, and then the Foundation could easily plug that information into the CMS.
</p>

