<.decorative_heading tag="h3" style="simpler">Additional Work</.decorative_heading>

<p>
  In addition to the website, I also coded an HTML email for the Foundation to promote their five year anniversary. The email was tested through Litmus to ensure it looked good across a number of different email clients, and was deployed from MailChimp.
</p>

<.decorative_heading tag="h3" style="simpler">Outcome</.decorative_heading>

<p>
  Our team at BIG YAM created a robust WordPress build that provided a fresh look for The Bob & Renee Parsons Foundation, and gave their team the tools to easily update content for years to come. In particular, the streamlined grant eligibility flow helped to manage intake for potential grant recipients while also making it easier for organizations to apply for funding.
</p>
